{"tid":156393,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又死9隻]遊巴失控撞路邊攤　9死14傷","createTime":"2017-03-14T16:39:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-14T16:39:23.000Z","uid":32407,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a293a57b52f7d9f0af94034803e6bd573a200ddf","tid":156393,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T16:39:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170314/bkncn-20170314151435961-0314_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170314%2Fbkncn-20170314151435961-0314_05011_001.html&d=S%2BP5iCTdX9iTDztVuYOIb2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=8b2a40b7\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170314/bkncn-20170314151435961-0314_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170314/photo/bkncn-20170314151435961-0314_05011_001_01b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170314%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170314151435961-0314_05011_001_01b.jpg&h=a646c3d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n山東青州市邵莊鎮今早發生一宗致命車禍，一輛小型旅遊巴失控撞向路邊攤檔，造成少23人受傷，其中5人重傷。救援人員接報到場將傷者送院救治，其中4人送院途中不治。濰坊市公安局交警支隊經初步調查，指肇事旅巴司機「操作失誤」釀成事故，已排除其他人為因素。目前，肇事旅巴司機已被扣查。<br />\n<br />\n事發在今早9時許，從現場拍到的片段可見，事故現場攤檔貨品散落一地，有車輛受波及，車頭嚴重損毀。多人受傷倒地，救援人員趕緊將傷者抬上車送院。<br />\n<br />\n及至晚上近8時，官方通報5名重傷送院的傷者經搶救無效死亡，令事故的死亡人數增至9人；另有14人正在醫院治療，暫無性命危險。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}